    {
      "id": "l10-vehicles",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Transport words",
      "body": "# Getting around\n\nWays to travel:\n\n- **Train** (रेलगाड़ी) · **Bus** (बस) · **Car** (गाड़ी) · **Plane** (हवाई जहाज़)\n- **Ticket** (टिकट) · **Road** (सड़क) · **Airport** (हवाई अड्डा) · **Luggage** (सामान)\n\nIn English we travel **by** a vehicle: *by train* (रेलगाड़ी से), *by bus* (बस से), *by car* (गाड़ी से). The word **by** does not change. One exception: we say *on foot* (पैदल), not *by foot*."
    },
