    {
      "id": "l10-phrases",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Travel phrases",
      "body": "# At the station\n\nPhrases that help you travel:\n\n| English | Hindi |\n|---|---|\n| Where is the bus? | बस कहाँ है? |\n| One ticket, please. | एक टिकट, कृपया। |\n| I want to go to the airport. | मुझे हवाई अड्डे जाना है। |\n| Stop here, please. | यहाँ रोकिए, कृपया। |\n\nTo tell a driver your destination, use **I want to go to the ...** : *I want to go to the airport* (मुझे हवाई अड्डे जाना है). End requests with **please** (कृपया) to stay polite."
    },
